The paper discusses the importance of software engineering practices and metrics in scientific research, indicating a focus on software development. The Metrics Dashboard is a platform for producing and observing metrics for software development projects, indicating a focus on software engineering and project management. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.SE (Software Engineering). Other likely sub-categories include cs.CY (Computational Geometry), cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), cs.PL (Programming Languages), and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
